               <msContents>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <rubric>Nomina sacra; name of the scribe; names of the donors (in a secondary hand); groups of lines in the incipit page of Texts I-1; incipit of sections and subsections; elements of the punctuation signs and of the text dividers; elements of Ethiopic numerals.</rubric>
                     <incipit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </explicit>
                     <note/>
                  </msItem>
                  <!--The data in the items below refers to other items. please remove this items and move the information to the appropriate place.-->
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                     <note>Text I-1 includes the hymns:</note>
                     <note>- ʾƎsäggǝd läki ʾo-ʾǝgzǝʾtǝyä qǝddǝst dǝngǝl Maryam Mariham ʾǝmmu lä-ʾIyäsus Krǝstos kähali ... "I worship Thee, O my Lady, Holy Virgin Mary, Mother of Jesus Christ the Almighty ..." (fols. 7vb-8ra)</note>
                     <note>- Sälam läki ʾo-ʾǝgzǝʾtǝyä Maryam dǝngǝl ʾǝmmä mädḫǝn ǝmmä bǝrhan ... "Salutation to you, o my Lady, Virgin Mary, Mother of the Saviour, Mother of the Light ..." (fol. 8ra-va).</note>
                     <note/>
                     <note>All miracles of Mary (Text I-4) are numbered. Miracles 21, 22 and 23 are followed by a poem:</note>
                     <note>- fol. 30rb:</note>
                     <note>ዛካርያስ፡ ርእየ፡ በወርኃ፡ ሳባጥ፡ በሠርቁ።</note>
                     <note>ተአምረኪ፡ ለዘይት፡ ማዕከለ፡ ፪ኤ፡ አዕፁቁ።</note>
                     <note>ማርያም፡ ጽዮን፡ ለብርሃን፡ ተቅዋመ፡ ወርቁ።</note>
                     <note>ዕዝራኒ፡ በገዳም፡ አመ፡ ወዓለ፡ ውዱቁ።</note>
                     <note>ለኅብረ፡ ገጽኪ፡ ጽጌ፡ ሐተወ፡ መብረቁ።</note>
                     <note>(= a strophe from the Maḫletä ṣǝge "Canticle of the Flower", cp. GrohHymn p. 78).</note>
                     <note>- fol. 31ra:</note>
                     <note>ታቦተ፡ አምላከ፡ ፳ኤል፡ ጽዮን፡ ማርያም፡ ዘነገደት፡ ምድረ፡ ኢሎፍሊ።</note>
                     <note>ወቀጥቀጠቶ፡ ለዳጎን፡ ነፍሳተ፡ ብዙሃን፡ ማኅጐሊ።</note>
                     <note>አመ፡ ነገደት፡ ቍስቋም፡ በኃይለ፡ ወልዳ፡ ከሃሊ።</note>
                     <note>ወድቁ፡ አማልክተ፡ ግብፅ፡ መናብርተ፡ ሰይጣን፡ ሀባሊ።</note>
                     <note>ወተኃፍሩ፡ ኵሎሙ፡ {ዘቦሙ፡} አስጋሊ።</note>
                     <note>- fol. 31vb:</note>
                     <note>እስከ፡ መነነቶ፡ ሚልኮል፡ ቅድመ፡ ታቦተ፡ ሕግ፡ አመ፡ ዘፈነ።</note>
                     <note>ንጉሠ፡ ፳ኤል፡ ኪያኪ፡ ዘጸገየ፡ ስነ።</note>
                     <note>ቅድመ፡ ገጸ፡ ሥዕልኪ፡ እንዘ፡ እዘፍን፡ አነ።</note>
                     <note>ዘይሜንን፡ ተአምረኪ፡ ወሰብሐተኪ፡ ቍርባነ።</note>
                     <note>በአፈ፡ መላእክት፡ ወሰብእ፡ ለይኩን፡ ምኑነ።</note>
                     <note/>
                     <note>Text I-4 concludes with a supplication for the scribe.</note>
                  </msItem>
